<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />God, you have taught me from my youth;</para>

<para style="q1">even now I declare your wonderful deeds.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />Indeed, even when I am old and gray-headed, God, do not forsake me,</para>

<para style="q1">as I have been declaring your strength to the next generation,</para>

<para style="q1">your power to everyone who is to come.</para>
